model.name: Miao2010 - Innate and adaptive immune responses to primary Influenza A Virus infection_1

body.div: Model 1 of the Miao et. al. 2010. This model cannot be readily simulated. The model requires time course arrays of parameters values of A_G, A_M and T_E. This feature is not implemented.

div.p: This model is hosted on BioModels Database and identified by: BIOMD0000000546.
To cite BioModels Database, please use: BioModels-15 Years of Sharing Computational Models in Life Science.
